{"tid":321130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻醉強迫小貓剃毛紋身 狂男炫耀施虐：小貓很酷","createTime":"2017-07-14T05:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T08:11:58.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9678849801213e1ca3ee7df25648703ac2532634","tid":321130,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170713/large/1499951944_c196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170713%2Flarge%2F1499951944_c196.jpg&h=76ab0ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山東濟寧一名經營紋身店的男子，早前竟剃光買來的小貓右腳腳毛，繼而在腳上練習紋身。昨日網上流傳男子拍攝的影片，即時引起網民狠批。涉事男子強子(化名)隨後向傳媒解釋，替小貓紋身並非有意，承認自己犯錯，已將小貓送到小動物救助站，以求外界原諒。<br />\n<br />\n據網上相片，強子在小貓剃光毛的右腳紋上一大片花紋，以及一個「忍」。強子後來還拍攝一段小貓被紋身後的影片，在微信朋友圈調侃和炫耀。影片即時引起愛護動物人士憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，強子向傳媒表示，自己在濟寧開紋身店已經7年，小貓是自己花30元人民幣買來的，養了好幾個月了。幾天前，自己忽然想到為小貓紋身。由於覺得紋身是一種藝術，遂剃光小貓右前腿上的毛，在表皮敷上麻醉藥，便替小貓紋身。強子指出，待小貓麻醉藥退卻，自己就給牠喝點水就沒事了。<br />\n<br />\n紅星新聞/新浪微博"},{"pid":"dafec9f0f97c18d5cb9e740af0c73b63f8931ebf","tid":321130,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd59e7e980d2ef46876b700c39166134748cf19d","tid":321130,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人死硬係唔見呢啲仆街死"},{"pid":"e41fd854ce6c2dd837bfde3986ea7cf58890a6b5","tid":321130,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"係鬼國做貓都慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88a51fad913e691c29219074ed86ec1dd483bd4","tid":321130,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁多人死硬係唔見呢啲仆街死</blockquote><br />\n算好架啦<br />\n普通支那人會食撚埋落肚"},{"pid":"f62dfc89b546766d5b3c570ae91d4f6523944be8","tid":321130,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"拎佢碌鳩黎紋 屌你老母"},{"pid":"67c110db159925f05e5307c9a1ecbd4efa18c5f3","tid":321130,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"紋完無煮來食 算有良心"},{"pid":"df3aec378faf8cbe33fc9c429ae736158b0927c9","tid":321130,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"強子紋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87374d7c2d2a413e74bfa0278861f8f2df360b36","tid":321130,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"無煮黎食算係咁啦"},{"pid":"4f9bea29faa77eb42bfbb52000ba867df6ef3aaa","tid":321130,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"咁浪費食物真係過份"},{"pid":"04246b580f74ac3f668385dcc9662dbc4394287b","tid":321130,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"做咗七年都仲要練習都唔荒好得去邊"},{"pid":"b51794e94983477c1fd3b427bde1a90f4054c446","tid":321130,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:37:17.000Z","msg":"敷左麻醉藥係咪都會好痛？"},{"pid":"d3006c5a0eb741f67e82d40cfd175e00ca8f093b","tid":321130,"uid":3952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"紋身有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebab274db06da57436c733b34a164647d71d2caf","tid":321130,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紋身有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國人做咪有問題"}]}